snippet.textDisplay: Sharing such pure cultures is the only way to mitigate the political enmities between India and Pakistan. When singers like RFAK sing for those 6:44 minutes, a person however cruel will surely forget whether he is from India or Pakistan and just say one word.....WOW INCREDIBLE. Music is a divine power to bring peace, which is the sole purpose of ISLAM. Singers like RFAK and Momina always prove it. Even if India and Pakistan keep fighting for another 200 years, but for those 200 years talents from India and Pakistan will be respected from both sides, which is enough to end the ANGER. Love from India, Salute to RFAK and Momina.
